 obtained by using the $n=10$ blob model. We also compare our\nresults with those obtained by using single-blob models with state-dependent\npotentials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Sep 2014 13:46:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-07"}
